headline.print_headline: Sears Worker in Upstate New York Dies After Shelves Collapse
headline.main: Sears Worker in Upstate New York Dies After Shelves Collapse

lead_paragraph: A Sears employee in northern New York has died of injuries suffered when storage racks at the store collapsed and pinned him underneath, authorities said.
